  {
    "id": "7630110270908472846",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Now on view at Modern Edge Gallery: Water Memory by Sarah Nelson. Photography and installation, in the main gallery through the fall. Come see it in Nob Hill.",
    "created_at": "2025-11-28T18:30:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000002358",
    "like_count": "33",
    "retweet_count": "5",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "quote_count": "3"
  },
  {
    "id": "4408366949483465527",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Opening night for Water Memory was a full house. Thank you Albuquerque. Two vessels already found homes.",
    "created_at": "2025-11-29T04:15:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000002489",
    "like_count": "179",
    "retweet_count": "54",
    "reply_count": "3",
    "quote_count": "3"
  },
  {
    "id": "6136429430006661554",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "First Friday this week — we are open late for the Nob Hill art walk, 5 to 8. Wine, work, and good company.",
    "created_at": "2025-10-28T21:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000002620",
    "like_count": "211",
    "retweet_count": "19",
    "reply_count": "9",
    "quote_count": "5"
  },
  {
    "id": "4523615007047343814",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Big news I can finally share: I have a solo show opening at the Southwest Arts Museum in Santa Fe on October 17. The title is Vessel as Landscape.",
    "created_at": "2025-11-10T16:20:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000002751",
    "like_count": "245",
    "retweet_count": "35",
    "reply_count": "12",
    "quote_count": "5"
  },
  {
    "id": "5499109077439154920",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Studio day. Coil-building the tallest vessel yet for the museum show, 38 inches and still climbing.",
    "created_at": "2026-03-14T17:45:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000002882",
    "like_count": "67",
    "retweet_count": "17",
    "reply_count": "5",
    "quote_count": "2"
  },
  {
    "id": "3849799550657125539",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Gallery hours this week: Wednesday through Sunday, 11 to 6. Stop in and sit with the Water Memory pieces.",
    "created_at": "2025-12-14T15:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000003013",
    "like_count": "52",
    "retweet_count": "10",
    "reply_count": "10",
    "quote_count": "1"
  },
  {
    "id": "7266851738029871981",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "New work from the roster just landed at the gallery. Marcus Oliver's welded steel piece is stopping people in the doorway.",
    "created_at": "2025-10-15T19:10:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000003144",
    "like_count": "52",
    "retweet_count": "17",
    "reply_count": "5",
    "quote_count": "5"
  },
  {
    "id": "7452394956427150613",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Artist talk Saturday at 2: Sarah Nelson on water, memory, and working between photography and installation. Free, seats are limited.",
    "created_at": "2025-11-18T14:30:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000003275",
    "like_count": "32",
    "retweet_count": "5",
    "reply_count": "7",
    "quote_count": "4"
  },
  {
    "id": "1953907606524429468",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Reminder that Modern Edge represents 18 New Mexico and Southwest artists. If you are building a collection, come talk to us.",
    "created_at": "2026-03-27T18:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000003406",
    "like_count": "36",
    "retweet_count": "11",
    "reply_count": "1",
    "quote_count": "5"
  },
  {
    "id": "1749893333159332060",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Pulled a kiln load this morning. The reduction surface on Vessel number 8 came out exactly like the arroyo I was chasing.",
    "created_at": "2026-03-16T15:20:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000003537",
    "like_count": "261",
    "retweet_count": "74",
    "reply_count": "10",
    "quote_count": "6"
  },
  {
    "id": "9138023291631979682",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Catalog proofs for Vessel as Landscape are in. Seeing the work laid out as a series makes the whole thing feel real.",
    "created_at": "2025-11-06T20:40:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000003668",
    "like_count": "144",
    "retweet_count": "32",
    "reply_count": "7",
    "quote_count": "6"
  },
  {
    "id": "9466332060412082343",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "We are open for First Friday tonight. New pieces in the front room and Sarah's Water Memory in the main gallery.",
    "created_at": "2026-01-01T22:30:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000003799",
    "like_count": "42",
    "retweet_count": "2",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "quote_count": "3"
  },
  {
    "id": "6055047051523223989",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Slow morning at the wheel with coffee and the light coming through the casita windows. Best part of the job.",
    "created_at": "2026-02-24T15:05:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000003930",
    "like_count": "63",
    "retweet_count": "9",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "quote_count": "1"
  },
  {
    "id": "5211718930653734403",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Delivery and install for the museum show is October 16. Crating twelve vessels is its own kind of art project.",
    "created_at": "2025-10-19T16:45:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000004061",
    "like_count": "268",
    "retweet_count": "15",
    "reply_count": "2",
    "quote_count": "3"
  },
  {
    "id": "7115241323848670672",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Thank you to everyone who came out for the Water Memory opening. Sarah's work deserves every bit of it.",
    "created_at": "2025-11-29T17:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000004192",
    "like_count": "105",
    "retweet_count": "13",
    "reply_count": "4",
    "quote_count": "1"
  },
  {
    "id": "2806704990377735377",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "If you missed First Friday, the gallery is open all weekend. Water Memory runs through the fall.",
    "created_at": "2025-12-04T16:10:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000004323",
    "like_count": "241",
    "retweet_count": "31",
    "reply_count": "11",
    "quote_count": "2"
  },
  {
    "id": "1382485058918556598",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Loading the truck for a studio-to-gallery run. The Tacoma has hauled more clay than I can count.",
    "created_at": "2025-10-08T14:50:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000004454",
    "like_count": "163",
    "retweet_count": "47",
    "reply_count": "11",
    "quote_count": "4"
  },
  {
    "id": "3477535800039283915",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Every vessel in Vessel as Landscape starts as a coil the width of my thumb. Then a few hundred more.",
    "created_at": "2026-03-22T18:35:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000004585",
    "like_count": "134",
    "retweet_count": "20",
    "reply_count": "7",
    "quote_count": "6"
  },
  {
    "id": "2569398676975433103",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Wall text and labels for the museum show are drafted. Curator meeting next week to lock the checklist.",
    "created_at": "2025-11-16T19:25:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000004716",
    "like_count": "79",
    "retweet_count": "5",
    "reply_count": "10",
    "quote_count": "0"
  },
  {
    "id": "7116812693878689619",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Kiln at cone 10 and the whole casita smells like hot clay. Albuquerque studio days are the best days.",
    "created_at": "2026-03-06T16:00:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000004847",
    "like_count": "35",
    "retweet_count": "1",
    "reply_count": "12",
    "quote_count": "2"
  },
  {
    "id": "1856603934019208902",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "glaze test tiles out of the electric kiln. the cobalt wash pooled better on the textured ones, noting that for the big vessels",
    "created_at": "2026-02-22T23:10:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000004978",
    "like_count": "193",
    "retweet_count": "45",
    "reply_count": "6",
    "quote_count": "6"
  },
  {
    "id": "2351810730996798057",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "reduction firing tomorrow at ray's. the wood kiln takes three days and every hour of it, but nothing else gives you that surface",
    "created_at": "2025-10-16T02:40:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000005109",
    "like_count": "315",
    "retweet_count": "29",
    "reply_count": "11",
    "quote_count": "1"
  },
  {
    "id": "2455053265296783857",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "spent the afternoon trimming feet on six pots. meditative until it isn't",
    "created_at": "2026-03-11T22:15:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000005240",
    "like_count": "218",
    "retweet_count": "29",
    "reply_count": "10",
    "quote_count": "0"
  },
  {
    "id": "7449709879791707586",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "clay planet order arrived, fresh stoneware and a fresh bag of cobalt carbonate. studio restocked",
    "created_at": "2026-02-27T18:20:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000005371",
    "like_count": "155",
    "retweet_count": "38",
    "reply_count": "8",
    "quote_count": "0"
  },
  {
    "id": "7385235246905586050",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "the slab roller finally paid for itself this week. built two test panels in the time it used to take for one",
    "created_at": "2025-10-03T17:30:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000005502",
    "like_count": "217",
    "retweet_count": "53",
    "reply_count": "3",
    "quote_count": "5"
  },
  {
    "id": "4696346960128194805",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "watching the kiln cool is the hardest patience in ceramics. no peeking until it is under 300",
    "created_at": "2026-03-19T13:45:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000005633",
    "like_count": "222",
    "retweet_count": "53",
    "reply_count": "9",
    "quote_count": "6"
  },
  {
    "id": "2200783773959226303",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Sending preview images of Vessel as Landscape to a few collectors this week. Helen, this one is for you.",
    "created_at": "2025-11-09T15:40:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000005764",
    "like_count": "99",
    "retweet_count": "30",
    "reply_count": "5",
    "quote_count": "0"
  },
  {
    "id": "6702661781155249522",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Grateful for the folks who back this work early. A studio visit turned into a commission today.",
    "created_at": "2025-10-22T20:05:00+00:00",
    "lang": "en",
    "reply_to_tweet_id": "1780000000000005895",
    "like_count": "131",
    "retweet_count": "14",
    "reply_count": "3",
    "quote_count": "5"
  },
  {
    "id": "4747452062514959399",
    "author_id": "4595523313641464983",
    "text": "Framing out the fall calendar: Water Memory now, the Santa Fe museum show in October, and a group show after.",
